  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to investigate a possible role of dreaming in emotion regulation
      testing whether dreaming of a close relative recently deceased is correlated with a positive
      evolution of the bereavement process
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
